<%
	provide(:full_width, "true")
	provide(:title, "Home")
%>

<div class="jumbotron">
	<div class="container">
            <h1>Weekly roundtables of Lean Entrepreneurs</h1>
            <p>In theory there is no difference between theory and practice; in practice there is. You can read books, blogs, watch videos, or you can join a weekly session where your ideas can be challenged by a group of your peers working on the same issues day in day out. You choose.</p>
	  <% if current_peer %>
	  	<p><%= link_to "Complete your application &raquo;".html_safe, registration_peer_path(current_peer), class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %></p>
	  <% else %>
	  	<p><%= link_to "Request an invite &raquo;".html_safe, new_peer_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %></p>
	  <% end %>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="container">
	<div class="row">
	  <div class="col-sm-4">
	    <h2 class="feature-title">Accountability</h2>
	    <p>Each week you will get to pick a learning goal and make a commitment for the following session that you have to update the group about.</p>
	  </div>
	  <div class="col-sm-4">
	    <h2 class="feature-title">Ongoing help</h2>
	    <p>Every week you have an opportunity to share the biggest problem in your business and get help with it.</p>
	 	</div>
	  <div class="col-sm-4">
	    <h2 class="feature-title">Tactics & Tools</h2>
	    <p>Learn about specifc tools and tactics other members have used to solve problems you're now facing.</p>
	  </div>
	</div>
</div>
